file.name: openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: App
  version: 1.0.0
servers: []
paths:
  '/:username':
    get:
      summary: Get user by user name
      responses:
        '400':
          responseCode: 400
          description: User not found
        default:
          description: lol
      operationId: httpHandler
      parameters:
        - description: The name that needs to be fetched. Use user1 for testing.
          required: true
          in: path
          schema:
            type: string
          name: username
      tags:
        - JAJA
        - Framework
        - NodeJS
        - Deno
        - Hello2
        - Hello3
        - Hello
components:
  schemas: {}
  responses: {}
  parameters: {}
  examples: {}
  requestBodies: {}
  headers: {}
  securitySchemes: {}
  links: {}
  callbacks: {}
tags:
  - name: Framework
    description: .NET
  - name: NodeJS
    description: Runtime
